'''Bronisław Baczko''' (June 13, 1924 – August 29, 2016)<ref>[http://wyborcza.pl/1,75398,20617564,bronislaw-baczko-nie-zyje-byl-wybitnym-filozofem-znawca-oswiecenia.html Bronisław Baczko nie żyje. Był wybitnym filozofem, znawcą oświecenia, historykiem myśli społecznej] {{pl icon}}</ref> was a Polish [[philosopher]] and [[historian of ideas]]. Together with [[Leszek Kołakowski]], he was a leading figure in the [[Warsaw School (history of ideas)|Warsaw School]] of the history of ideas in the late 1950s and 1960s.

== Prizes and honours ==
* 2011: [[Balzan Prize]] for his work on the [[Age of Enlightenment]]

