{{Infobox philosopher |region = [[Western philosophy]] |era = [[Contemporary philosophy|21st century Philosophy]] |color = |image = |name = '''François Raffoul''' |birth_date = 1942 |birth_place = Lyon |death_date = |death_place = |school_tradition = [[Continental philosophy|Continental]] |main_interests = [[Existentialism]], [[hermeneutics]] |notable_ideas = |influences = |influenced = }}
'''Françoise Dastur''' (born 1942 in [[Lyon]]) is a French philosopher. She is Professor Emeritus at [[University of Nice Sophia Antipolis]].<ref>[http://www.babelio.com/auteur/Francoise-Dastur/5181 Françoise Dastur]</ref><ref>French Women Philosophers. A Contemporary Reader, Christina Howells, 2004</ref><ref>[http://www.paris-art.com/evenement-culturel/Rencontres%20philosophiques.%20Le%20corps,%20chose%20insens%C3%A9e/Dastur-Fran%C3%A7oise/3097.html Rencontres philosophiques. Le corps, chose insensée]</ref>
